about.summary: Simple generic functions (similar to Python's own len(), pickle.dump(), etc.)

name: simplegeneric
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.8.1" %}

package:
  name: simplegeneric
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: simplegeneric-{{ version }}.zip
  url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/s/simplegeneric/simplegeneric-{{ version }}.zip
  md5: f9c1fab00fd981be588fc32759f474e3

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - simplegeneric

about:
  home: http://cheeseshop.python.org/pypi/simplegeneric
  license: Zope Public License
  summary: "Simple generic functions (similar to Python's own len(), pickle.dump(), etc.)"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - minrk
    - msarahan
    - pelson
